reviewText: I cannot believe my eyes - I just had to say something regarding the amount requested by the seller (new for $1,499.99).  Wow! goes through my mind especially when I don't know what I'll be purchasing or what's on the DVDs.  Did not see listing of episodes or titles.  What exactly does "Dragnet: 20 Big Episodes" include.  Needs a list so I can make an educated judgment.  Unlikely and unwise to spend so much on unknown merchandise in my opinion.
